WEBVTT

00:02.896 --> 00:04.689
- VERN: My story is one
as old as time.

00:04.793 --> 00:05.965
- You're Burnin' Vernon.
- That's me.

00:06.068 --> 00:07.793
The guy from the '90s,
sang that one song.

00:07.896 --> 00:11.000
My descent down to rock bottom
was just as swift.

00:11.103 --> 00:12.965
After jail,
I recruited my buddy Walt

00:13.068 --> 00:15.724
to help me impersonate
a preacher.

00:15.827 --> 00:18.482
I needed some quick cash to pay
off my baby mama, Debbie,

00:18.586 --> 00:20.379
for my 15-year-old daughter,
Charlotte.

00:20.482 --> 00:21.758
Say what?

00:21.862 --> 00:24.000
Debbie's boyfriend, Ronnie,
got himself blown up.

00:24.103 --> 00:25.965
Debbie was left
with a little secret.

00:26.068 --> 00:27.000
- I'm pregnant.

00:27.103 --> 00:28.551
- VERN: I found myself
back in jail.

00:28.655 --> 00:30.241
- This sucks.
- VERN: Like I said,

00:30.344 --> 00:31.793
it's a tale as old as time.

